            <a href="#" style="color: #006699; text-decoration: none;">Background</a><br />
            <a href="#" style="color: #006699; text-decoration: none;">Mission and vision</a><br />
            <a href="#" style="color: #006699; text-decoration: none;">About us</a>
        </td>
        <td style="width: 33%; vertical-align: top; padding: 10px;">
            <h3 style="color: #00FF00;">COMPANY ACTIVITIES</h3>
            <a href="/Minerals" style="color: #006699; text-decoration: none;">Minerals</a>
